OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F421A1780503064
OL,3,CNissan announce intention to make cars
OL,4,Cfor Chinese manufacturer Chery in UK
OL,6,FNissan have announced a plan which
OL,7,Fcould see them making cars for
OL,8,Fmanufacturer Chery at their Sunderland
OL,9,Fplant.
OL,11,FThe two companies have signed a non-
OL,12,Fbinding agreement to look into a
OL,13,Fcontract that would see the Chinese
OL,14,Fcompany's vehicles being made in the
OL,15,FNorth East for sale on the UK market.
OL,17,FThis could begin as early as 2027.
OL,19,FThe facility in Sunderland would still
OL,20,Fbe owned by Nissan, and staff would
OL,21,Fremain as the company's employees.
