OL,3,CNissan announce intention to make cars
OL,4,Cfor Chinese manufacturer Chery in UK
OL,6,FIn May, Nissan said they planned to
OL,7,Fmerge two production lines into one in
OL,8,Fa bid to "secure better plant
OL,9,Futilisation", meaning one production
OL,10,Fline is now free to make vehicles for
OL,11,FChery.
OL,13,FMassimiliano Messina, Nissan's
OL,14,FChairperson for Africa, Middle East,
OL,15,FIndia, and Oceania region said: "This
OL,16,Fis an important step forward for our
OL,17,Foperations.
