OL,3,CNissan announce intention to make cars
OL,4,Cfor Chinese manufacturer Chery in UK
OL,6,F"We are looking forward to working
OL,7,Fwith Chery International UK in the
OL,8,Fcoming months to finalise a position
OL,9,Fthat is optimal for both companies."
